      "header": "The Chase",
      "body": [
        "After the 26th race of the season, the players in the top 10 in points are automatically qualified for The Chase. In addition, there are two \"wild card\" qualifiers, specifically the two players with the most race wins who are ranked between 11th and 20th in points.",
        "Players who qualify for The Chase will have their point totals reset to 5,000 points. The 10 automatic qualifiers receive a bonus of 10 points for each race win during the regular season, while the two wild cards receive no such bonus. The scoring for the remaining 10 races is the same as the first 26 races."
      ]
